Package model

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ModelAPI
    Interface representing main model component of the Vector Racer system, it is the game data and logic.
    PlayerAPI
    Interface which represents a player in the game.
    RacerAPI
    Interface representing a Racer in the game.
    RacetrackAPI
    Interface representing a racetrack in the game.
    Terrain
    Interface which represents terrain characteristics in the game.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AIPlayer
    Class representing an AI player in the game.
    AirTile
    Class which represents an air tile in the game.
    CheckpointTile
    Class representing a checkpoint tile in the game.
    IceTile
    Class which represents an ice tile in the game.
    Model
    Class representing an instance of the ModelAPI, all backend data and logic, the game itself.
    Move
    Represents a move in the game.
    Player
    Class which represents a player in the game.
    Racer
    Class representing a racer in the game.
    Racetrack
    Class representing a racetrack in the game.
    SandTile
    Class which represents a sand tile in the game.
    State
    Class which represents a game state in which the current game players, racetrack, and AI mode are held.
    Tile
    Abstract class which represents a tile in the game.
    WallTile
    Class which represents a wall tile in the game.
